nodes.name: Trigger
nodes.helpText: Send a static message. Can also be triggered from other flows

nodes.name: Throttle
nodes.helpText: Slow down the incoming messages so that one is emitted at each occurrence of the specified interval

nodes.name: Compose
nodes.helpText: Wait for all values to be received before sending the message

nodes.name: Demultiplex
nodes.helpText: Break an array of values into discreet messages
